# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s24a_11abd621:

    # "Las Vegas appears on the horizon far before we actually reach it. Clusters of generic skyscrapers are interspersed with the world-famous casinos, which come in many shapes and sizes."
    "Las Vegas aparece en el horizonte mucho antes de que realmente lleguemos. Grupos de rascacielos genéricos se intercalan con los casinos de fama mundial, que vienen en muchas formas y tamaños."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s24a_5ac66f87:

    # "Some are indistinguishable from the tall banks and offices around them, except for gaudy logos and signs."
    "Algunos son indistinguibles de los altos bancos y oficinas que los rodean, excepto por los logotipos y letreros llamativos."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s24a_676537ac:

    # "Others are constructed to look like a pyramid, or a Roman palace, or a medieval castle."
    "Otras están construidas para parecer una pirámide, o un palacio romano, o un castillo medieval."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s24a_296833a0:

    # "There’s a distinct clash where some buildings are striking and clean looking, as if they’d just been completed yesterday."
    "Hay un contraste marcado donde algunos edificios son llamativos y de aspecto limpio, como si se hubieran terminado ayer."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s24a_f4c87c6b:

    # "But then just beside them will be a sad looking place with faded paint and signs that aren’t supposed to be flickering."
    "Pero justo al lado hay un lugar triste con pintura descolorida y letreros que no deberían estar parpadeando."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s24a_b89589d8:

    # "As we enter the city limits, we’re suddenly surrounded by the noise of traffic and the smell of exhaust. Exiting the highway was like crossing the boundary to another world."
    "Al entrar en los límites de la ciudad, de repente nos rodea el ruido del tráfico y el olor a escape. Salir de la autopista fue como cruzar la frontera hacia otro mundo."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s24a_d4e9528a:

    # "Marina drinks it all in."
    "Marina lo absorbe todo."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s24a_4e3028fc:

    # Marina "Ooh, what’s that one? The super tall one!"
    Marina "Охх, а это что? Супер высокое!"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s24a_77c4fdc8:

    # "She points through the windshield. Even though it’s impossible to follow her finger, I know which one she’s talking about."
    "Señala a través del parabrisas. Aunque es imposible seguir su dedo, sé de cuál está hablando."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s24a_c88788a2:

    # Amber "That’s the Stratosphere. I think it’s one of the tallest buildings in the country."
    Amber "Это Стратосфера, я думаю это одно из высочайших зданий в стране."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s24a_d63ea5e6:

    # Marina "Whoa…"
    Marina "Вау…"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s24a_89a45e6e:

    # "We’re still miles out, but she already seems to be infatuated with the city. Her eyes are wide and so is her mouth."
    "Todavía estamos a kilómetros de distancia, pero ya parece estar fascinada con la ciudad. Tiene los ojos muy abiertos y la boca también."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s24a_e7a86e12:

    # Amber "It’s even cooler up close."
    Amber "Оно еще круче вблизи."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s24a_1637f356:

    # Marina "I never knew cities could be this… huge."
    Marina "Я никогда не думала, что города могут быть такими… огромными."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ffb50e41:

    # "I keep forgetting that she’s never been out of New Mexico. Sure, there are couple decently sized cities there, but nothing this impressive."
    "Sigo olvidando que nunca ha salido de Nuevo México. Claro, hay un par de ciudades de buen tamaño allí, pero nada tan impresionante como esto."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s24a_e210281f:

    # "I’m excited for her to experience all this for the first time."
    "Estoy emocionada de que experimente todo esto por primera vez."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ea83b624:

    # Amber "Honestly, Las Vegas is kind of on the small side, at least compared to places like New York or Chicago."
    Amber "Честно говоря, Лас-Вегас не очень большой, особенно в сравнении с такими городами как Нью-Йорк и Чикаго."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ae3e8c3a:

    # Marina "Seriously? That’s insane…"
    Marina "Серьезно? Это невероятно…"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s24a_6a5f278a:

    # Marina "I can’t imagine that many people in one place."
    Marina "Я даже не могу представить, такое огромное количество людей в одном месте."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s24a_38351255:

    # Amber "What about your house?"
    Amber "Ну а как насчет дома, где вы живете всей семьей?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s24a_8f6c5e0e:

    # "She giggles."
    "Ella ríe entre dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s24a_7ab3cc1f:

    # Marina "That’s pretty close."
    Marina "Ну да, там было похоже."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s24a_b0da42cb:

    # "She reminds me of a puppy, straining against its leash as she whips between looking out the windshield and out the passenger-side window."
    "Me recuerda a un cachorro, tirando de su correa mientras se mueve entre mirar por el parabrisas y por la ventana del acompañante."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s24a_cd997269:

    # "To me, the part of the city that we’re in looks like any other downtown area, so I’m not impressed. Once we get to The Strip, where all of the really famous casinos are located, it’ll be different."
    "Para mí, la parte de la ciudad en la que estamos se ve como cualquier otro centro urbano, así que no me impresiona. Una vez que lleguemos a The Strip, donde están todos los casinos realmente famosos, será diferente."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s24a_3cf7b830:

    # "But first I have another destination in mind."
    "Pero primero tengo otro destino en mente."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ecc252cf:

    # Amber "So Mare."
    Amber "Итак, Мари."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s24a_49341fc0:

    # Marina "Yeah?"
    Marina "Да?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s24a_c70b35aa:

    # Amber "Ever heard of the World Carnival Buffet? At the Rio?"
    Amber "Ты когда-нибудь слышала о Мировом Карнавальном Буфете? В Рио?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s24a_3e6c813c:

    # Marina "I don’t think so. Should I?"
    Marina "Не думаю. А должна была?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s24a_62dce57e:

    # Amber "Well if you like food, it’s pretty much the greatest place on Earth."
    Amber "Ну что ж, если ты любишь поесть, то это лучшее место на земле."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s24a_29ad204e:

    # Amber "They have like, everything imaginable to eat. And lots of stuff that you can’t imagine either."
    Amber "У них есть любая еда, которую ты только можешь себе представить и целое море того, о чем ты даже не слышала."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s24a_f4584c4d:

    # "Somehow, her eyes get even wider."
    "De alguna manera, sus ojos se abren aún más."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s24a_c04d787a:

    # Marina "I wanna try it all."
    Marina "Я хочу попробовать все."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ecde0653:

    # Amber "Pretty sure you’ll change your mind when you see some of it. But that’s the spirit!"
    Amber "Я почти уверена, что ты изменишь свое мнение, когда увидишь некоторые из них. Но это отличный настрой!"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s24a_402a80a5:

    # Marina "Are we going there now?"
    Marina "Мы едем туда прямо сейчас?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s24a_114b55fa:

    # Amber "Hell yeah we are. I’m starving."
    Amber "Черт побери да. Я жутко голодна."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s24a_86aa7504:

    # Marina "Me too!"
    Marina "Я тоже!"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s24a_7292ca25:

    # "And she grabs my free hand; the one that isn’t on the steering wheel."
    "Y agarra mi mano libre; la que no está en el volante."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:160
translate spanish hwb_s24a_4b3662da:

    # "My heart leaps to my throat."
    "El corazón se me sube a la garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ee8904c4:

    # "Since we’re at a red light I catch her eye and she smiles, though her face is a little red."
    "Como estamos en un semáforo en rojo, la miro a los ojos y ella sonríe, aunque tiene la cara un poco roja."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s24a_a7181b5c:

    # "I smile back but then face forward."
    "Le devuelvo la sonrisa, pero luego miro al frente."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s24a_f5d8ac77:

    # "Our hands hang limply between our seats. It isn’t long before our palms are moist with sweat. I don’t know whose."
    "Nuestras manos cuelgan flojamente entre los asientos. No pasa mucho tiempo antes de que nuestras palmas estén húmedas de sudor. No sé de quién es."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s24a_80abc6c7:

    # "Her hand is so soft. Like she treats it with lotion or something, but I know that’s not the case."
    "Su mano es tan suave. Como si la tratara con loción o algo, pero sé que no es el caso."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s24a_2f104bdd:

    # "Smooth, like a baby’s."
    "Lisa, como la de un bebé."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s24a_53bfa48d:

    # "It makes me a little self-conscious of my chewed fingernails and chronically dry skin."
    "Me hace sentir un poco cohibida por mis uñas mordidas y mi piel crónicamente seca."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s24a_4a52bed3:

    # "Worried that I’m gonna gross her out and she’ll pull away or something."
    "Preocupada de que le dé asco y se aleje o algo."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:188
translate spanish hwb_s24a_6ff51b03:

    # Marina "Is this okay?"
    Marina "Все в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:192
translate spanish hwb_s24a_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "Хм?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s24a_acb9dcb8:

    # "Maybe I was getting a little too distracted."
    "Quizás me estaba distrayendo demasiado."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s24a_992500ff:

    # Amber "Is what?"
    Amber "О чем ты?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s24a_a39bbddb:

    # "She raises our linked hands."
    "Levanta nuestras manos entrelazadas."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:204
translate spanish hwb_s24a_da8eb6dd:

    # Marina "This."
    Marina "Это."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s24a_b3e2f125:

    # Marina "You just seemed kinda…"
    Marina "Ты выглядишь так…"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s24a_33772887:

    # Marina "Like, I mean, I can not, if you-"
    Marina "В смысле, я могу перестать. Если тебе-"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:214
translate spanish hwb_s24a_9b3bb143:

    # Amber "No! No, it’s fine. Seriously."
    Amber "Нет! Нет, все в порядке. Серьезно."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s24a_782eb57c:

    # "I’m talking louder than I need to, flustered as I try to backpedal. She doesn’t look convinced."
    "Estoy hablando más fuerte de lo necesario, nerviosa mientras intento retroceder. No parece convencida."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:220
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ae810673:

    # Marina "Okay. Sorry, I’m still… You know. Not really…"
    Marina "Ладно. Извини я все еще… ты знаешь. Не совсем…"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:224
translate spanish hwb_s24a_a048c5fa:

    # Amber "It’s fine. You’re fine. Really."
    Amber "Все хорошо. И ты хорошая. Серьезно."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:228
translate spanish hwb_s24a_d56ea741:

    # Amber "I’m the one who should be sorry. I’m not usually this weird in a relationship."
    Amber "Это я должна извиняться. Обычно я не веду себя так странно в отношениях."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:232
translate spanish hwb_s24a_2107ff97:

    # "Now she looks almost offended."
    "Ahora parece casi ofendida."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s24a_61fae46f:

    # "Crap."
    "Rayos."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s24a_a63b9727:

    # Amber "Not like that! I just mean-"
    Amber "Я не совсем это хотела сказать! Я имела ввиду-"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s24a_6cbd594e:

    # "A blaring honk from behind reminds me that I’m sitting stopped at a green light."
    "Un bocinazo ensordecedor desde atrás me recuerda que estoy detenida en un semáforo en verde."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s24a_fd36996b:

    # "The middle of traffic isn’t the best place for this conversation."
    "El tráfico no es el mejor lugar para esta conversación."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s24a_9f3499ae:

    # "Breathing deeply as we pull ahead, I try to collect my thoughts."
    "Respirando hondo mientras avanzamos, intento ordenar mis pensamientos."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s24a_1f35a116:

    # Amber "Sorry. Again. I just… Have a lot on my mind. Because I like you! I really do! You know that really freaking well by now!"
    Amber "Извини. Снова. Я всего лишь… Нужно о многом подумать. Потому что ты мне нравишься! Правда! Знаешь сейчас я правда очень сильно волнуюсь!"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s24a_eeec592e:

    # "She smiles, though she’s still looking down. And our hands are still together."
    "Sonríe, aunque sigue mirando hacia abajo. Y nuestras manos siguen juntas."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s24a_fd5b148b:

    # "And this is such an awkward time and place to be talking about this."
    "Y este es un momento y lugar tan incómodos para hablar de esto."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s24a_9f2ad043:

    # Amber "So it’s my bad if I’m being weird or whatever. But being with a girl I met on the side of the road is a new one, even for me, you know?"
    Amber "Так что это я виновата, в том что веду себя странно, или что-то вроде того. Но знаешь быть с девушкой которую я встретила на дороге странно, даже для меня, понимаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s24a_8f51fd96:

    # "Finally, she laughs."
    "Finalmente, se ríe."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s24a_dc9d4dce:

    # Marina "Yeah, I guess it’s a little weird."
    Marina "Да, я думаю это довольно странно."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s24a_317d36bb:

    # "I feel like I can still hear a slight quiver in her voice, but I might be imagining it."
    "Siento que aún puedo oír un leve temblor en su voz, pero quizás me lo imagino."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s24a_5180dbc3:

    # "So I squeeze her hand tightly. Immediately, she squeezes back."
    "Así que aprieto su mano con fuerza. Inmediatamente, ella me devuelve el apretón."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s24a_23ce135a:

    # "I only have a vague idea of the direction I need to be driving. Fortunately, it isn’t too long until the Rio comes into view, looming large a few miles away."
    "Solo tengo una idea vaga de la dirección que debo tomar. Por suerte, no pasa mucho tiempo hasta que el Río aparece a la vista, imponente a unas millas de distancia."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s24a_26ae2840:

    # "We pull into the parking lot near the back, where the only open spaces are left."
    "Nos estacionamos en el lote cerca de la parte trasera, donde solo quedan espacios libres."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s24a_03b092e2:

    # "It’s pleasantly warm outside. I’ve heard stories of people’s shoes melting on the asphalt during the summer. But for now the weather’s perfect."
    "Afuera hace un calor agradable. He oído historias de gente que se derrite los zapatos en el asfalto durante el verano. Pero por ahora el clima es perfecto."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s24a_ae59a4e7:

    # "As we cross through the parking lot towards the casino, Marina takes my hand yet again."
    "Mientras cruzamos el estacionamiento hacia el casino, Marina toma mi mano una vez más."

# game/script/hwb_s24a.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s24a_8c1a53c2:

    # "I can feel my heart rate accelerate, but I squeeze her fingers all the same."
    "Siento que mi ritmo cardíaco se acelera, pero aprieto sus dedos de todas formas."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s24a.rpy:298
    old "Crossing the parking lot"
    new "Crossing the parking lot"

